{"word":"H2818 - חֲשַׁח - chăshach - khash-akh' - Careful","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חֲשַׁח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>chăshach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khash-akh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Careful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தேவையாயிரு, அவசியமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"as a verb:"},{"paragraph":"1) (P'al) to need, to have need"},{"paragraph":"as a noun:"},{"paragraph":"2) (P'al) the thing needed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> (Chaldee); a collateral root to one corresponding to <a href=\"#/H2363 - חוּשׁ - chûwsh - koosh/2363\">H2363</a> in the sense of <i>readiness</i>; to <i>be necessary</i> (from the idea of <i>convenience</i>) or (transitively) to <i>need: - </i>careful, have need of."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2818 - חֲשַׁח - chăshach - khash-akh'/2818\">H2818</a>, <a href=\"#/H2819 - חַשְׁחוּת - chashchûwth - khash-khooth'/2819\">H2819</a>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}